snippet.title: Freddy & Friends: On Tour Episode 2
snippet.description:
This week’s installment of “Freddy & Friends: On Tour!” was found in the Fazbear Entertainment archives! Our best minds have digitized these episodes for your viewing pleasure! Grab a slice of pizza and hang out with your friends Freddy, Chica, and Bonnie.
